videos.headline: Jabrill Peppers scores on 3-yard TD run
videos.description: Wolverines' Jabrill Peppers gets the snap and rushes for a 3-yard touchdown, tying the game for Michigan against Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jabrill Peppers scores on 3-yard TD run) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Michigan takes the lead with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: De'Veon Smith run for 1-yard for a TD

videos.headline: Spartans control the clock on first score
videos.description: Michigan State RB LJ Scott scores on a 5-yard touchdown run as the Spartans control the clock in the first quarter against Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Spartans control the clock on first score) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Michigan dances into the end zone for 1-yard run
videos.description: Michigan's De'Veon Smith gets the toss and dances his way for a 1-yard touchdown during the second quarter against Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Michigan dances into the end zone for 1-yard run) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Spartans kicker connects on a 52-yard FG
videos.description: Michigan State kicker Michael Geiger connects with a 52-yard field goal, cutting the Spartans' deficit to four points against the Wolverines.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Spartans kicker connects on a 52-yard FG) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Speight and Darboh connect for 43-yard pass for Wolverines
videos.description: Michigan QB Wilton Speight finds Amara Darboh down the field for a 43-yard pass which would eventually set up Michigan for a field goal against Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Speight and Darboh connect for 43-yard pass for Wolverines) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Michigan pushes the pile for a 5-yard TD
videos.description: Wolverines' De'Veon Smith runs through the middle and pushes his way into the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown against the Spartans.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan pushes the pile for a 5-yard TD) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Late INT before half helps Wolverines' momentum
videos.description: Michigan's Jourdan Lewis picks off Michigan State QB Tyler O'Connor with 27 seconds remaining in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Late INT before half helps Wolverines' momentum) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Michigan State gets interception to start second half
videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight gets intercepted by Michigan State's Darian Hicks and returns it for 42-yards during the third quarter.

videos.headline: Michigan's Darboh tops off his air game with a one-handed grab
videos.description: Michigan QB Wilton Speight sends a pass to Amara Darboh for a one-handed 39-yard catch against Michigan State.

videos.headline: Spartans not giving up and score a 20-yard TD in the fourth
videos.description: Michigan State QB Brian Lewerke connects with Monty Madaris for a 20-yard touchdown pass in the fourth quarter against Michigan to cut the deficit to 13.

videos.headline: Michigan's Peppers all over the field and signs off with a sack
videos.description: Michigan's Jabrill Peppers sacks Michigan State QB Brian Lewerke and stops him from converting a first down.

videos.headline: Spartans score a late TD
videos.description: Michigan State QB Tyler O'Connor completes a pass to Donnie Corley and sends him into the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown with a second to spare in the fourth quarter against Michigan.

videos.headline: Jabrill Peppers return for defensive PAT
videos.description: Jabrill Peppers return for defensive PAT

videos.headline: Jabrill Peppers excited after rivalry game win
videos.description: Jabrill Peppers does a backflip after Michigan's 32-23 win over Michigan State

videos.headline: Peppers is happy to go back to Ann Arbor with a win
videos.description: Michigan's Jabrill Peppers discusses his performance on all three phases of the game against Michigan State and how he was able to read the final play of the game where he returned a PAT for a defensive conversion.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Peppers is happy to go back to Ann Arbor with a win) 2016/10/29

videos.headline: Jabrill Peppers doing it all for Michigan
videos.description: Michigan's Jabrill Peppers was doing it all for the Wolverines, scoring on the offensive and defensive sides of the ball as well as recording a sack against Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Jabrill Peppers doing it all for Michigan) 2016/10/29 ESHEET
